728178f-a.text:
Vleigh Place, east side, at 75th Road, showing a farmhouse, owned by Henry Barlow from 1891 to 1909.  It no longer appears in a 1926 atlas of Queens.  When this area was modernized in the late 1930's it appears that Main Street was cut through the site of the house.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  1923
